code: import $api from"../http/index";export default class AuthService{static async login(email,password){const res=await $api.post('/auth/login',{email,password});return res.data;}static async registration(email,password,name){const res=await $api.post('/auth/registration',{email,password,name});return res.data;}static async logout(){const res=await $api.post('/auth/logout');return res.data;}static async checkAuth(){const res=await $api.get('/auth/refresh');return res.data;}static async sendResetPasswordEmail(email){const res=await $api.put('/auth/reset',{email});return res.data;}}
